metadata.name: Ukraine Chaos
metadata.description:
Nowadays yellow and blue are so precious colors. soul of loved ones who have been forced to fight or the ones who have been honored to resistance. Sometimes life is unacceptable and complicated, coming out of the blue and hitting people right in the middle of the eyebrows. The only thing you can do is to be the strongest you for today, Amine.

Dimensions: 2429x3363
